<para>
  Set the policy governing whether graphics windows will create new
  layers when new &images;, &skels;, or &meshes; are created.  The
  <varname>policy</varname> applies to newly created windows, not
  existing ones. Use the <link
  linkend="MenuItem-OOF.Graphics_n.Settings.New_Layer_Policy"><guimenu>Settings/New
  Layer Policy</guimenu></link> menu item in an existing graphics
  window to change its policy.
</para>

